Simple crawler notes

Implemented using Python 2.7 + scrapy framework



Refernce sites used

https://doc.scrapy.org/en/latest/intro/tutorial.html


Future steps

Investigate the Apache Nutch option from an enterprise framework

Change the visualisation method to feed the Json stream to an Elastic instance via the scrapy ELK extension

Extend the model to more effectively support asynch streaming via queue mechanism for receipt and processing of search results. Initial options under consideration Kafka, Redis, Rabbit